sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant API
    participant AuthService
    participant Service
    participant DB

    Client->>API: POST /test (Authorization, Body)
    API->>AuthService: Validate token

    alt Токен невалиден
        AuthService-->>API: Invalid
        API-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
    else Токен валиден
        AuthService-->>API: Valid
        API->>Service: Validate required fields

        alt Отсутствуют обязательные поля
            Service-->>API: Validation error
            API-->>Client: 400 Bad Request
        else Данные корректны
            Service->>DB: Create resource
            DB-->>Service: OK
            Service-->>API: 201 Created
            API-->>Client: 201 Created
        end
    end